Philip Stainton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_Stainton 0 Philip Stainton (9 April 1908 – 1 August 1961) was a British-born actor. Stainton appeared in several Ealing comedies. He often played uniformed policemen, he appeared in both British and Australian productions Philip_Stainton ( 9_April_1908 – 1_August_1961 ) was a_British-born_actor .
